OL,6,FMore than 360,000 train services
OL,7,Facross Britain were fully or part-
OL,8,Fcancelled in the past year as
OL,9,Freliability is at a joint record low
OL,10,Famid major staffing shortages.
OL,12,FPA news agency analysis of the latest
OL,13,FOffice of Rail and Road data found
OL,14,F208,000 services were fully axed in
OL,15,Fthe year to November 9.
OL,17,FA further 161,000 were part-cancelled,
OL,18,Fmeaning they did not serve at least
OL,19,Fone of their scheduled stops.
